Package svmapp

Class Summary
Chart Handles all the charting of the package, making use of the JFreeChart and JMathPlot libraries.
gen_parameter This class stores all of the parameters required for data generation in a single location, as well as providing two public static int variables specifying the types of data dependencies which can be generated.
Generator This class is responsible for storing training and validation sets, as well as generating them according to data dependencies.
GUI This class is responsible for constructing and handling the GUI.
IO This class handles all input/output.
SVMApp This is the top level class in the package containing the main() method which is executed at runtime.
SVMTrain This class is responsible for training, cross validation and test validation of a LIBSVM based SVM.
